{
  "stem": "23090.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When we arrived to Auschwitz--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not to my recollection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was loaded up, and there was-- not to my recollection, it was-- it didn't.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got in in the morning, into-- some time during the morning, because it was daylight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I just-- you couldn't describe it in any way if you wanted to do it in a horror movie, or in a novel, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The minute they opened the wagons, it was just total, complete misery.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Beatings, and screamings, and beatings, and barking of dogs, and raw growling of dogs, and whistles of trains, and screaming, and beating, and screaming.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And commands given.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was just-- it was just like, you open the doors, and all of a sudden, you find yourself in this inferno, in this, in this, in this unimaginable horror that you, as a adult or a child, would see in nightmares.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was just coming through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were just holding on to each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I don't know, within minutes, my mother and my sister were dragged to one side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was dragged with my dad to another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were told to go to another side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I never had a chance to say goodbye to my mother, never had a chance to say goodbye to my sister.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The, the, the, the pace, the speed of this, this thing, it was done by design.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was done to both-- for the person not to be able to comprehend, or understand, or in any way be able to think for a second what was happening.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was just incredible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was just an incredible situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
